{"tid":1227361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望阻一阻各位為香港好既朋友時間","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:46:37.000Z","uid":25148,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8d9c4769f31598cf1ebf86cbaa0e9cc89237ff","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:55:14.000Z","msg":"相信頭先大家都收到一個沉重既消息<br />\n已經有人為我地既社會犧牲咗自己既生命<br />\n我知大家而家心情都好低落<br />\n<br />\n  所以 我地唔可以辜負烈士既心意<br />\n我並唔係話當冇咗件事 但而家首要應做既<br />\n係推返啲有用既post上去 一齊漂漂亮亮咁贏一次<br />\n作為紀念依位無名烈士既禮物<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地唔知你係邊個 但大家都會記得你既付出<br />\n安息啦朋友<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月16 一齊迫爆個政總佢</span>"},{"pid":"a3275a42ab8e65660093f2f9f483a96018556921","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#223256 三角蚤 <br />\n我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfTV79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfTV79.png&h=d30c7c40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40e0a7781891b9c445a15beadea576c621a8a17c","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44ae0d959c66db6e21dd25735f7d5e6140c6c11","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4c853ef10d8d31d4e6cdb57234efedd0475e8d","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"有睇到既人 唔洗回應 做就得架喇"},{"pid":"0ce4e6b2f51f045fc33c0f237f99a83dfb830991","tid":1227361,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"有心既朋友 可以摺一朵紙花以表心意"},{"pid":"79dd6fddc8f50e7b94c157894fa5675cac0a2db8","ti